data.description: Welcome to a magnificent stucco & stone 2-story home nestled within a revered master-planned community adorned w/extraordinary amenities. With an open floor plan encompassing modern elegance, this residence boasts a thoughtfully designed layout & full home Kinetico water softener. The primary bedroom has just had new carpet installed & is complemented by an en-suite bath & walk-in closet. There are 3 add'l bedrms on the 2nd floor, ensuring ample space for family & guests. Having a private office down & game room up provides a great balance. Indulge in outdoor living w/an enticing kitchen, comprised of a built-in grill, sink, & mini-fridge, allowing for effortless al fresco dining ventures. With an on-site elementary school, educational opportunities are within easy reach for young residents, fostering a seamless balance between work & family life. Conveniently located w/fast access to I-10 & Grand Pkwy 99, commuting to nearby cities or exploring the greater Houston area is a breeze.
